OL,7,FA nurse working at a care home hit by
OL,8,Fa Covid outbreak in which seven
OL,9,Felderly residents died refused to wear
OL,10,Fa face mask as they believed the virus
OL,11,Fwas a conspiracy, an inquest has heard.
OL,13,FThe residents, who lived at Holmesley
OL,14,FCare Home in Sidford, Devon, all died
OL,15,Fin March or April 2021 having
OL,16,Fcontracted coronavirus.
