OL,7,FAlison Longhorn, area coroner for
OL,8,FDevon, Plymouth and Torbay, is holding
OL,9,Finquests into the deaths of William
OL,10,FWilkinson, 102, Doris Lockett, 92, Roy
OL,11,FGilliam, 96, Jean Hartley, 81, Susan
OL,12,FSkinner, 70, Ronald Bampfylde, 92, and
OL,13,FStdanislawa Koch, 93.
OL,15,FJemma Turner, the nursing home's
OL,16,Fdeputy manager and registered nurse,
OL,17,Ftold the hearing she was telephoned in
OL,18,Fthe early hours of 2 March 2021 by a
OL,19,Fcare worker saying there was a
OL,20,Fsuspected outbreak.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
