OL,3,CCare home nurse 'refused to wear mask
OL,4,Cas they believed Covid was a
OL,5,Cconspiracy'
OL,7,F"I told her I was on my way. I called
OL,8,Fanother staff member and asked if they
OL,9,Fwould come with me because I felt we
OL,10,Fpossibly had an outbreak of Covid in
OL,11,Fthe home."
OL,13,FMrs Turner said she started testing
OL,14,Fresidents on one floor of the home and
OL,15,Fall were positive.
OL,17,F"I thought, 'What am I going to do?'"
OL,18,Fshe said.
