OL,7,FShe explained another staff member
OL,8,Fthen questioned why she was testing
OL,9,Fall the residents.
OL,11,F"She said, 'Don't worry, we did it on
OL,12,FFriday, the tests were a bad batch `
OL,13,Fthey were all positive'," Mrs Turner
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"I asked her what did she mean, and
OL,17,Fshe said they were a bad batch. I
OL,18,Fdidn't think the manager would
OL,19,Fdisregard a positive test."
