OL,7,FThree days later, Mrs Turner contacted
OL,8,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC),
OL,9,FDevon safeguarding and the police with
OL,10,Fher concerns about the outbreak.
OL,12,F"No-one wanted to help me and I felt
OL,13,Fthe longer we leave it, residents
OL,14,Fcould potentially die," she said.
OL,16,F"I think I was on the phone a good
OL,17,Ffive or six hours."
