OL,7,FThe home guidelines said that if a
OL,8,Fstaff member tested positive, they
OL,9,Fshould be sent home, then any resident
OL,10,Fthey had been in close contact with
OL,11,Fmust be isolated for 14 days and all
OL,12,Fstaff and residents must be tested.
OL,14,FThe CQC had carried out two visits in
OL,15,Fthe February and told the home it was
OL,16,Fnot following guidelines for the use
OL,17,Fof PPE, the hearing at County Hall in
OL,18,FExeter was told.
