OL,7,FMrs Turner also alleged managers at
OL,8,Fthe home would tell staff lateral flow
OL,9,Ftests (LFTs) were negative when they
OL,10,Fwere in fact positive, would not show
OL,11,Fthem the tests, and would allow them
OL,12,Fto work.
OL,14,F"A staff member messaged me, and I
OL,15,Ftold her do not go to work because you
OL,16,Fare positive, go and do a PCR test,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,19,F"I asked another staff member about
OL,20,Fwhether he had a positive LFT and I
OL,21,Fasked him when that was done.
