OL,7,F"I think he said either that day or
OL,8,Fthe day before and I asked him if he
OL,9,Fhad been to work, and he said yes and
OL,10,Fsaid the manager said he could work."
OL,12,FMrs Turner said she had told the nurse
OL,13,Fwho believed coronavirus was a
OL,14,Fconspiracy that they were required to
OL,15,Fwear PPE.
