OL,7,F"The first time I spoke to him he
OL,8,Fexpressed his view of Covid was just a
OL,9,Fconspiracy and I explained that he
OL,10,Fcould have his personal view but he
OL,11,Fhad to keep that to himself and while
OL,12,Fworking with elderly people that are
OL,13,Ffrail and at risk he had to follow the
OL,14,Fguidelines," she said.
