OL,7,F"I said he knew the rules and needed
OL,8,Fto wear the mask, and we had not had
OL,9,Fany medical exemption."
OL,11,FShe said two days before the suspected
OL,12,Foutbreak the nurse had been
OL,13,Fcomplaining of feeling unwell but
OL,14,Fattributed it to tiredness and night
OL,15,Fworking.
OL,17,FMrs Turner said there was also a high
OL,18,Fturnover of staff at the nursing home,
OL,19,Fwhich she attributed to the heavy
OL,20,Fworkloads and low staffing levels.
