OL,7,FAsked for her overall impression of
OL,8,Fthat time, Mrs Turner replied: "Awful.
OL,9,FIt's sad for the residents.
OL,11,F"They should have passed away being
OL,12,Fcared for and I felt this could have
OL,13,Fbeen prevented.
OL,15,F"I also think that if I didn't go to
OL,16,Fthe police no-one would know this had
OL,17,Fpotentially happened."
