OL,7,FA nutritionist who worked at the home,
OL,8,FLouise Dolton, described how she
OL,9,Finitially thought the home had good
OL,10,FCovid practices in place in the months
OL,11,Fbefore the outbreak.
OL,13,FBut when she spoke to the police as
OL,14,Fthey investigated the outbreak, she
OL,15,Frecounted three instances in which
OL,16,Fstaff who had tested positive were
OL,17,Fasked not to leave.
