OL,7,FShe said a cook showed her a positive
OL,8,Ftest and asked to leave. The manager
OL,9,FJoe Birchall was alleged to have said
OL,10,F"But who is going to cook?". The cook
OL,11,Fdid however go home.
OL,13,FThe statement went on to say that on 5
OL,14,FMarch care lead Nicole Da Silva tested
OL,15,Fpositive and was told by the manager
OL,16,Fshe had done the test wrong. She did
OL,17,Fthree more, all of which were positive.
