OL,7,FThe inquest heard Ms Da Silva was told
OL,8,Fshe couldn't go home and was only
OL,9,Fallowed to go when she received a call
OL,10,Ffrom her son's nursery because her son
OL,11,Fwas not well.
OL,13,FMs Dolton said a third worker, who
OL,14,Flived on site, was told to isolate
OL,15,Fafter testing positive but she saw him
OL,16,Fworking a shift and was told he would
OL,17,Fonly be working in areas where
OL,18,Fpatients were positive.
